  "body": "### Description\r\nCurrently, enabling authentication forces all API Methods to be authenticated. It would be nice that enabling authentication for specific API methods, like ADMIN, was a feature. For example, calls to the more harmless methods like NET or ETH should not need authentication, however, calls to ADMIN methods should be authenticated.\r\n\r\n\r\n",
